APInvoicesImport.importSQLSelect: SELECT f.*,m.*, f.Document_Type,replace(\u0027Invoice_Type\u0027,\u0027_\u0027,\u0027 \u0027) as \u0027Sub_Class\u0027, s.docId FROM sysadm.AP_Invoices f INNER JOIN sysadm.FTBStorage m ON f.F_StorageID \u003d m.Storage_ID LEFT JOIN MWMigration s ON f.F_DocumentID \u003d s.F_DocumentID AND s.TableName \u003d \u0027AP_Invoices\u0027 and s.ObSeqNum \u003d 0 WHERE (s.Import_Date IS null OR s.status_detail is null or SUBSTRING(s.Status_Detail, 1, 2) \u003c\u003e \u0027OK\u0027) AND f.Indexed_Date \u003e\u003d \u0027?\u0027
APInvoicesImport.importDocTypeNumber: SELECT Type_ID FROM sysadm.FTBDocTypes WHERE Type \u003d \u0027AP_Invoices\u0027
APInvoicesImport.importSingleDocumentSQL: SELECT f.*,m.*,\u0027Invoice\u0027 as \u0027document_type\u0027,replace(\u0027Invoice_Type\u0027,\u0027_\u0027,\u0027 \u0027) as \u0027Sub_Class\u0027, s.docId FROM sysadm.? f INNER JOIN sysadm.FTBStorage m ON f.F_StorageID \u003d m.Storage_ID LEFT JOIN MWMigration s ON f.F_DocumentID \u003d s.F_DocumentID AND s.TableName \u003d \u0027AP_Invoices\u0027 and s.ObSeqNum \u003d 0 WHERE f.F_DocumentID \u003d ?
APInvoicesImport.successFullImportsSQL: select year(import_date), month(import_date), day(import_date), count(*) from mwmigration where import_date is not null and TableName \u003d \u0027?\u0027 and ObSeqNum \u003d 0 and status_detail \u003d \u0027OK\u0027 group by year(import_date), month(import_date), day(import_date) order by 1 desc, 2 desc,3 desc
APInvoicesImport.pendingImportsSQL: SELECT year(f.indexed_date), month(f.indexed_date), day(f.indexed_date), count(*) FROM sysadm.? f LEFT JOIN MWMigration s ON f.F_DocumentID \u003d s.F_DocumentID and s.TableName \u003d \u0027?\u0027 and s.ObSeqNum \u003d 0 WHERE (s.Import_Date IS null OR SUBSTRING(s.Status_Detail, 1, 2) \u003c\u003e \u0027OK\u0027) group by year(f.indexed_date), month(f.indexed_date), day(f.indexed_date) order by 1 desc, 2 desc,3 desc
APInvoicesImport.errorCountsSQL: select status_detail, count(*) from mwmigration WHERE TableName \u003d \u0027?\u0027 and ObSeqNum \u003d 0 group by status_detail order by 2 desc
APInvoicesImport.importComparisonSQL: SELECT ? f.*, s.docId FROM sysadm.? f INNER JOIN MWMigration s ON f.F_DocumentID \u003d s.F_DocumentID and s.TableName \u003d \u0027?\u0027 and s.ObSeqNum \u003d 0 order by s.Validated_Date, s.docId
APInvoicesImport.importDocIdsSQL: SELECT s.docId, f.F_DocumentID, \u0027Invoice\u0027 as \u0027document_type\u0027,replace(\u0027Invoice_Type\u0027,\u0027_\u0027,\u0027 \u0027) as \u0027Sub_Class\u0027, \u0027\u0027 as ObSeqNum from sysadm.? f LEFT JOIN MWMigration s ON f.F_DocumentID \u003d s.F_DocumentID AND s.TableName \u003d \u0027AP_Invoices\u0027 and s.ObSeqNum \u003d 0
APInvoicesImport.downloadSql: SELECT s.DIN, m.STORAGE_PATH + \u0027\\\\u0027 + f.F_FILENAME + \u0027.MAG\u0027 as \u0027FILENAME\u0027 FROM sysadm.? f INNER JOIN sysadm.FTBStorage m ON f.F_StorageID \u003d m.Storage_ID INNER JOIN MWMigration s ON f.F_DocumentID \u003d s.F_DocumentID and s.TableName \u003d \u0027?\u0027 and s.ObSeqNum \u003d 0 WHERE f.Indexed_Date \u003e\u003d \u00271994-01-01\u0027 order by f.INDEXED_DATE, s.DIN
